&=\frac{1}{\pi}\int_{-\pi}^{0} (-1) \sin(n x) \, dx +\frac{1}{\pi}\int_{0}^{\pi} (1) \sin(n x) \, dx\\
&=\frac{1}{\pi}{\Bigl[ \frac{1}{n}\cos(nx) \Bigr]}_{-\pi}^{0} -\frac{1}{\pi}{\Bigl[ \frac{1}{n}\cos(nx) \Bigr]}_{0}^{\pi}\\
