&=\frac{1}{\pi}\Bigl[ \frac{1}{n} -\frac{1}{n}\cos(n\pi) \Bigr] -\frac{1}{\pi}\Bigl[ \frac{1}{n}\cos(n\pi) -\frac{1}{n} \Bigr]\\
